cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is about video captioning, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and its intersection with machine learning and AI. The second most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which covers CV and its intersection with machine learning and AI. The third most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers general machine learning techniques. The fourth most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), which covers AI techniques and their applications. The fifth most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which covers multimedia processing and its intersection with machine learning and AI.
